{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/search-bar-always-visible-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1974,"date":"2022-12-02T23:41:27","date_gmt":"2022-12-02T23:41:27","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1974"},"modified":"2023-09-06T08:06:29","modified_gmt":"2023-09-06T08:06:29","slug":"search-bar-always-visible-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/search-bar-always-visible-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Make the search bar always visible (desktop and mobile)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"How to make the search bar always visible on Shopify - Dawn &amp; all free themes\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/q0uJEM4khyE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All Shopify free themes have access to a search functionality: a magnifying glass shaped search icon that when clicked opens a search bar, where you can then type whatever you&#8217;re looking for and any matching results among your store&#8217;s products will be shown to you . While a great tool for any store or page in the web, having to click the search icon before revealing the search bar is one click too much and a step that could simply be skipped. <br><br>Using this tutorial you&#8217;ll learn not only how to make the search bar permanently visible and accessible on desktop but also on mobile regardless of the device you&#8217;re using, using only copy and pasted code that will work on all free themes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Depending on what version your theme is, you&#8217;ll need a different approach. Below we cover how to achieve it on the older (7 and below) and newer (7.0.1 and above) of all Shopify&#8217;s free themes.<br><br><a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview of the end result.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"NoticeBox NoticeBox--info\"><p>This tutorial is compatible only with Shopify&#8217;s official free themes: <b>Dawn, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origin, Spotlight, Publisher, Sense &amp; Craft.</b></p></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-1-adding-the-code-snippet\">1. Adding the code snippet</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Open your Shopify admin and navigate to <strong>Online Store &gt; Themes &gt; Actions &gt; Edit Code</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Under <strong>snippets</strong> on the left side, click on &#8220;add a new snippet&#8221;.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add a snippet named <strong>ezfy-header-search</strong> and paste this code inside:<br><br>[gist]e819355d5b3af9beb11c5d12ccd543af[gist]<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1084\" height=\"456\" class=\"wp-image-1995\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6.png\" alt=\"Creating the ezfy-header-search.liquid snippet file in the code editor\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6.png 1084w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6-850x358.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_6-768x323.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1084px) 100vw, 1084px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Save the file.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Now open the file named <strong>header.liquid</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Next we&#8217;ll implement the snippet into this file. <br><br>To proceed, double check your theme&#8217;s version to ensure it works correctly.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-2-a-steps-for-versions-above-7-0-1\">2.a. Steps for versions above 7.0.1</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Open your Shopify admin and click <strong>Online Store &gt; Themes &gt; Actions &gt; Edit Code &gt; Snippets &gt; Add a new snippet</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find the file <strong>header.liquid</strong> and open it</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Press <strong>CTRL + F</strong> (or <strong>CMD + F</strong> on <strong>Mac</strong>) to open the search bar and paste exactly this:<br><br><code><em>{% render 'header-search'</em></code><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Delete the line you found.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1118\" height=\"774\" class=\"wp-image-2997\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/a1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/a1.jpg 1118w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/a1-850x588.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/a1-768x532.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1118px) 100vw, 1118px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste the following:<br><br><code>{% render 'ezfy-header-search', input_id: 'Search-In-Modal', device: 'desktop' %}</code><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1172\" height=\"758\" class=\"wp-image-2999\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x2.jpg 1172w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x2-850x550.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x2-768x497.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1172px) 100vw, 1172px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Now press <strong>CTRL + F</strong> (or <strong>CMD + F</strong> on <strong>Mac</strong>) again to open the search bar and paste exactly this:<br><br><em>&nbsp;&lt;/header&gt;</em><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste the following code <strong>below </strong>the line you found.<br><br><code><em>{% render 'ezfy-header-search', input_id: 'Search-In-Modal', device: 'mobile' %}</em></code><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"923\" height=\"788\" class=\"wp-image-3001\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x3.jpg 923w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x3-850x726.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/x3-768x656.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 923px) 100vw, 923px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>That is it! You can skip the step <strong>2.b</strong> if your theme is above 7.0.1.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-2-b-steps-for-versions-below-or-equal-7-0-1\">2.b. Steps for versions below or equal 7.0.1</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In case your theme is below or equal the version 7.0.1, please do the following:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Inside the <strong>header.liquid </strong>file, press <strong>CTRL + F</strong> (or <strong>CMD + F</strong> on <strong>Mac</strong>) to open the search bar and search for:<br><br><code><em><code>&lt;details-modal class=\"header__search\"</code>&gt;</em></code><br><br>Paste the following code <strong><em>above </em></strong>the line you found:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-header-search', device: \"desktop\" %}</code><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1114\" height=\"541\" class=\"wp-image-2001\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8.png\" alt=\"Finding the location of the header__search in the header.liquid file\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8.png 1114w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8-850x413.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_8-768x373.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1114px) 100vw, 1114px\" /><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"509\" class=\"wp-image-2003\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_9.png\" alt=\"Adding the &quot;include&quot; liquid tag in the header.liquid file\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_9.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_9-768x460.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Repeat the search from step 4 but this time click &#8220;next&#8221; twice to find the second and final instance of the search icon deeper down into the file. <br><br>Again, right <strong><em>above </em></strong>it, paste the following:<br><br><code>{%- if section.settings.logo_position != 'top-center' -%}<br>{% include 'ezfy-header-search', search_type: 'desktop' %}<br>{%- endif -%}</code><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"590\" height=\"524\" class=\"wp-image-2005\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_10.png\" alt=\"Finding the location of the header__search in the header.liquid file\"><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"627\" height=\"548\" class=\"wp-image-2007\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_11.png\" alt=\"Adding the &quot;include&quot; liquid tag in the header.liquid file\"><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Finally, open the search bar a third time and search for the following:<br><br><code>&lt;/header&gt;</code><br><br>Right <strong><em>below </em></strong>that line, paste the following:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-header-search', device: 'mobile' %}</code><br><br>And you&#8217;re done! Don&#8217;t forget to click the &#8220;save&#8221; button on the top right of the screen.<br><br> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"499\" height=\"529\" class=\"wp-image-2010\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_12.png\" alt=\"Finding the header closing tag in the header.liquid file\"><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1021\" height=\"536\" class=\"wp-image-2012\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13.png\" alt=\"Saving the header.liquid file\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13.png 1021w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13-850x446.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_13-768x403.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1021px) 100vw, 1021px\" /></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You and your clients can now search your store more easily with a single click!<br><br>Before:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1340\" height=\"420\" class=\"wp-image-2015\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15.png\" alt=\"Default search icon in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15.png 1340w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15-850x266.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15-1200x376.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_15-768x241.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1340px) 100vw, 1340px\" /><br><br>After:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1339\" height=\"408\" class=\"wp-image-2017\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14.png 1339w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14-850x259.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14-1200x366.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_14-768x234.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1339px) 100vw, 1339px\" /><br><br>It works regardless of the logo position you have selected:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1344\" height=\"453\" class=\"wp-image-2020\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16.png 1344w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16-850x286.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16-1200x404.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_16-768x259.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1344px) 100vw, 1344px\" /><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1344\" height=\"432\" class=\"wp-image-2022\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17.png 1344w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17-850x273.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17-1200x386.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_17-768x247.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1344px) 100vw, 1344px\" /><br><br>And also on mobile:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"395\" height=\"399\" class=\"wp-image-2024\" style=\"width: 1600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot_18.png\" alt=\"Always visible search bar in Dawn theme, mobile\"><br><br>If you found any issues during or you&#8217;d like your search bar to be customized further, just send us an email at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> and we&#8217;ll be ready provide further guidance and offer a quote. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps\">&#8211; How to make slideshow images stop cutting off</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UKO9ViFXaWQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\">&amp;lt;br>&amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial&#8221; target=&#8221;_blank&#8221; rel=&#8221;noreferrer noopener&#8221;>- Add a collection tabs slider to any store (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)&amp;lt;/a>&amp;lt;iframe width=&#8221;560&#8243; height=&#8221;315&#8243; src=&#8221;https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc&#8221; title=&#8221;YouTube video player&#8221; frameborder=&#8221;0&#8243; allow=&#8221;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&#8221; allowfullscreen=&#8221;&#8221;>&amp;amp;amp;lt;br>&amp;amp;amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps&#8221;>- Disable right click, image and text copying and improve your store&#8217;s security&amp;amp;amp;lt;/a></iframe><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; How to add a collection with tabs section to any theme (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\"><br><br></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Make it so the search bar is always visible without the need for clicking the search icon every time. Works on all free themes including Dawn.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2037,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[655,626,657,435,776,773,663,649,652,646,660],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["Colorblock Theme","Craft Theme","Crave Theme","Dawn Theme","origin theme","publisher theme","Refresh theme","Ride theme","Sense Theme","Studio Theme","Taste theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/studio-slider-3-2.png","featured_image_url_alt":"Make the search bar always visible on all themes blog post image","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1974"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1974"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1974/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3286,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1974/revisions/3286"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/2037"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1974"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=1974"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=1974"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["330429198","3356652627"]}